{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"1308","heading":"Interagency agreement","label":"1308 Interagency agreement","identifier":"/us/usc/t47/s1308","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t47/ch12","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft47%2Fs1308","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["References in TextThis section, referred to in subsec. (b)(1), was in the original “this Act”, which was translated as meaning , div. FF, title IX, , , to reflect the probable intent of Congress.section 904 of Pub. L. 116–260134 Stat. 3214Dec. 27, 2020","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Broadband Interagency Coordination Act of 2020 and as part the Consolidated Appropriations Act, 2021, and not as part of the Broadband Data Improvement Act which comprises this chapter."],"amendments":["References in TextThis section, referred to in subsec. (b)(1), was in the original “this Act”, which was translated as meaning , div. FF, title IX, , , to reflect the probable intent of Congress.section 904 of Pub. L. 116–260134 Stat. 3214Dec. 27, 2020"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Short title","label":"a Short title","identifier":"/us/usc/t47/s1308/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t47/s1308","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft47%2Fs1308%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"This section may be cited as the “Broadband Interagency Coordination Act of 2020”.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Interagency agreement","label":"b Interagency agreement","identifier":"/us/usc/t47/s1308/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t47/s1308","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft47%2Fs1308%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","num